  "description": "HAMMER fixed at 0.0 — the neutral zone. Two VA voices in pure coexistence, filter link engaged, breathing in unison. Neither STRIFE nor LOVE. The treaty is not absence of conflict but its suspension. Both voices run through linked filters, breathing at the physiological rate of 0.067 Hz. A held note becomes a meditation on non-violence between identical forces.",
